      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_02-smr018.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ、勢いでいけるかもしれないな～って……\n仕方ないですね、今は下げておきます",
